              "type": "table",
              "content": "\\begin{tabular}{|l|c|c|c|c|c|c|c|}\\hline Day & Mon & Tue & Wed & Thu & Fri & Sat & Sun \\\\ \\hline Maximum temperature ($^\\circ\\text{C}$) & 8 & 12 & 15 & 14 & 11 & 7 & 4 \\\\ \\hline Minimum temperature ($^\\circ\\text{C}$) & 5 & -2 & -4 & -1 & -3 & & \\\\ \\hline\\end{tabular}"
