          ]
        },
        {
          "label": "(c)",
          "marks": 4,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "content": "These are the opening times for the museum.\nMonday to Friday $09\\ 00$ to $17\\ 00$\nSaturday and Sunday $10\\ 00$ to $16\\ 00$\nDuring opening hours the museum has $4$ security guards working.\nEach guard works a maximum of $30$ hours each week.\nWork out the smallest number of guards needed each week."
